    public abstract class AbstractApp
extends org.apache.wicket.protocol.http.WebApplication
    Common WebApplication ancestor for the example applications. Every application has two example pages: an AbstractFinalPage subclass that also serves as home page and an AbstractPrivatePage subclass.
    Author:
    akiraly
